  "title": "Site Engineer #78274",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Site Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Islandwide</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon to Fri 8am - 6pm, Sat 8am - 12pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $4,000 + Allowances + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Execute, monitor and ensure the timely completion of the project</li><li>Liaise with the Consultant Representative on project matters.</li><li>Coordinate with all Subcontractors on matters pertaining to site and quality issues;</li><li>Co-ordinate with QAQC Engineer to ensure quality performance of project to meet customer requirements.</li><li>Check for quality of work according to specification and requirement;</li><li>Maintain inspection records of works, materials and all completed works;</li><li>Ensure the site operations comply with the Project Quality Plan, including quality, environmental and occupational health & safety.</li><li>Review project specifications, technical clarification and construction drawings.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Civil or Structural Engineering</li><li>Has 1 year of site engineering experience</li><li>Willing to travel around Singapore from site to site</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78274 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
